  "description": "This individual is a compact, middle-aged bartender with bronze skin and brown eyes set beneath a heavy brow. Brown hair is kept in a plain, close-cropped cut that emphasizes a squared jaw and prominent cheekbones. Broad hands show permanent thickening at the knuckles, consistent with long service behind a bar, and a small, well-healed split along the lower lip marks an old impact injury. The overall physiognomy conveys durable health, practiced watchfulness, and a temperament formed by constant public-facing labor.",
